distribution? Collectivization of the non-monetary 
generation of profit? Liberation from the societal 
pressure towards profit maximization? If the com-
pulsion to siphon off surplus value is structurally 
rooted everywhere throughout society, albeit in dif-
ferent forms, then it is obviously no longer suffi-
cient to make a basic decision under economic con-
